{"tid":1630184,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［春袋］事實證明政府真係好撚驚你搞豪宅區","createTime":"2019-10-06T11:41:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T04:59:15.000Z","uid":91967,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"082fb49b24996a233d41c511e58d9dbd9b11d91f","tid":1630184,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:41:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8RJRWNU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8RJRWNU.png&h=73a2e70c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ee6DBNV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fee6DBNV.png&h=b152380f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日無論半山定係九龍塘<span style=\"color: red;\">一開始就佈重防</span>，往北既遊行隊伍被逼向深水埗/九龍城（佢地唔care既地區）方向走。<br />\n<br />\n但係，班狗根本<span style=\"color: red;\">冇可能封哂成個區</span>，大家可以見到有好多小路啲狗都冇封到。<br />\n<br />\n(如果仲有下次) 大家未必駛跟原定遊行路線，可以以目的地作目標，以自己方法<span style=\"color: red;\">到達再遊擊</span>。"},{"pid":"a29fa01a5ac0fdc68d411749d693c05b20d171d6","tid":1630184,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:41:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06c87e6c27b279168f844261fefbd62ff1b44da9","tid":1630184,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:42:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9204bc0bfa5c8ae8a68fedf55fe01ecda9e98f5","tid":1630184,"uid":61396,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:42:56.000Z","msg":"政要 高官<br />\n有錢佬<br />\n<br />\n先係地產霸權 核心<br />\n<br />\n卒仔（黑警）打兵仔（人民）<br />\n話知你死"},{"pid":"ac9a4304d4ec6b590786980e8421170eb1c26bcf","tid":1630184,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:18:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c211300fd55cba531ac0be203c8766f9047b9b9","tid":1630184,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:19:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj